\id 2JN - Tuivang Holy Bible 
\h 2 JOHAN 
\toc1 2 Johan 
\toc2 2 Johan 
\toc3 2 Johan 
\mt1 2 JOHAN  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 A hqamca ing, ak thlak tyk nu ingkaw awitak awh kai ing ka lungnaak a cakhqi - kai doeng am nawh, awitak ak simkhqi boeih boeih a venawh,  
\v 2 ningnih awh awm nawh ningnih a venawh kumqui dy ak awm awitak awh.  
\v 3 Pa Khawsa ingkaw Pa a Capa Jesu Khrih a venawh qeennaak, thin tlawhnaak ingkaw ngaihqepnaak taw ningnih a venawh awitak lungnaak ing awm kaw.  
\v 4 Pa ing ningnih awi a ni peek khqi amyihna, nangmih ca thlang vang ing awitak awh ami ceh a dawngawh zeelnaak ak bau soeih ce ni pehy.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt Joh 13.34; 15.12,17.\x*Tuh ka lungnaak nu, awipeek ak thai am qee law nyng ak cyk ca awhkawng ni taak uh awipeek ce ni ka mi qee law hy. Pynoet ingkaw pynoet lung qunaak aham thoeh law nyng.  
\v 6 Lungnaak taw ak awipeek ngainaak ing ni ceh ve ni.  
\v 7 Jesu Khrih taw pumsa na law hy tice amak do, ak qaai kqawn thlang khawzah, khawmdek benna cet kang hawh uhy. Cemyih ak thlang taw ak qaai kqawn thlang ingkaw Khrih a qaal ni.  
\v 8 Na bibi ce hlawng kaana laksawng ce ak soep na nami huhnaak aham ngaihta lah uh.  
\v 9 U awm haina dawng nawh Khrih a cawngpyinaak awh amak awm poe taw Khawsa am tahy, u awm cawngpyinaak awh ak awm poe taw Pa ingkaw Capa ce ta haih hy.  
\v 10 Nangmih a venawh vawhkaw cawngpyinaak taak kaana ak law thlang ce na ipkhui na koeh ceh pyi.  
\v 11 U awm cemyih ak thlang ak do taw anih a bibi amak leek ak pyikung na awm hy.  
\v 12 Nangmih a venawh ca khawzah qee aham ta hlai nyng, catlap ingkaw cahang tui hawnaak ham am ngaih nyng. Ce anglakawh, kaimih a zeelnaak a soepnaak thai aham nangmih a venna law nyng mik huh qoe na awi kak kqawn ngaih nyng.  
\v 13 Ak tyk nang a nanu a cakhqi ing kut ni tlaih uhy.   